      "description": "Presenting an absolute showroom-standard vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector's eye. This car is in pristine, flawless condition, having been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paintwork is breathtaking, featuring a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every panel alignment is factory-perfect. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather seats remain firm and supple with no bolster wear or creasing, and the high-gloss trim is free of any micro-scratches. All onboard technology, including the premium audio system and navigation, operates with 'day-one' precision. Mechanically, this car is peerless, accompanied by a comprehensive, paper-trail-documented service history performed exclusively by master technicians. The engine bay is detailed and spotless, and the undercarriage remains as clean as the day it was manufactured. This is not just a used car; it is a time-capsule quality vehicle for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection. Includes all original keys, window sticker, and bespoke floor mats.",
